OL,3,CLib Dem MP Cameron Thomas has whip
OL,4,Csuspended 'pending police probe'
OL,6,FA Liberal Democrat MP has had the whip
OL,7,Fsuspended pending the outcome of a
OL,8,Fpolice investigation, a party
OL,9,Fspokesperson said.
OL,11,FCameron Thomas was arrested by
OL,12,FGloucestershire Police on Wednesday
OL,13,Fnight, it is understood.
OL,15,FHis office has been contacted for
OL,16,Fcomment.
OL,18,FA Lib Dem spokesperson said the party
OL,19,Fwas "unable to comment further" while
OL,20,Fan "investigation is ongoing".
