OL,3,CLib Dem MP Cameron Thomas has whip
OL,4,Csuspended 'pending police probe'
OL,6,FMr Thomas' party membership is also
OL,7,Funderstood to have been suspended.
OL,9,FThe former RAF officer has served as
OL,10,FMP for Tewkesbury since the 2024
OL,11,Fgeneral election.
